                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer">Asmat prayer, “I Beseech You Lest I die Early,” <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተማኅፀኩ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይሙት፡ ዘእንበለ: ጊዜየ:</foreign></title>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.16"><locus from="53r" to="53v" facs="055"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer">Asmat prayer of Our Lord Jesus Christ</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">አስማተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘኅቡዕ፡ ወዘገሐ[ድ]፡ ስለደዊ፡ ተደያዊ፡ መቅደያዊ፡ አቤቱያዊ፡ ፍናልያዊ፡ አልልያይ: ታቦርያዊ:<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
